values:
NOT A CARD FROM EITH-ER OF THEM AND DONT YOU TELL ME THAT OTHER UN-I-VERSE EXCUSE.

BUT AM I BOTH-ERED! READ MY LIGHTS! DO I LOOK BOTH-ERED!

HAD SOME OLD PALS TURN UP. THEY HAD JUST DROPPED INTO THE NEIGH-BOUR-HOOD. THEN THEY HAD TO ALL GO OFF SOMEWHERE. ALL ALONE AGAIN FOR A WHILE. BUT THEY LEFT ME A NEW ROOM-MATE. VERY-BRIT-ISH-CYBER-MAN, SHE INSISTED WE DRINK TEA AND HAS PUT UP A PIC-TURE OF THE QUEEN. SHE WANTED US TO SING THE NAT-ION-AL AN-THEM BEFORE DINNER THEN CRIED WHEN WE DID. I'M NOT SURE ABOUT HER, I SHOULD HAVE MOVED IN WITH THE AUTON DOWN THE ROAD.

HOW ODD! JUST GOT A POST-CARD FROM ROSE! AND I WAS FEELING FOR-GOTT-EN! MAYBE SHE WANTED TO COME BACK TO ME!
<lj-cut> BUT THEN FOUND OUT THAT SHE IS BACK WITH THE MICK-EY! THEY MET UP AT A BIG FAMILY RE-UN-ION. OH THE DISS-A-POINT-MENT!
EVEN PLAGUE ZOM-BIES GET HUGS FROM ROSE AND THE DOC-TOR. NO ONE EV-ER WANTS TO HUG THE DA-LEK!
ANOTHER POSTCARD FROM ROSE. THE DOC-TOR HAS HAD A MAKE-OV-ER! BUT SHE DOESNT LIKE THIS NEW LOOK! SIDEBURNS AND DRY SKIN! EX-FOL-I-ATE!
HAVE DECIDED TO CHANGE CAREERS. TV PRO-DUCT-ION SOUNDS GOOD! REAL-ITY PRO-GRAMMING! I CAN PRETEND TO BE A NEW KIND OF CAMERA!
POST-CARD FROM ROSE. GLOAT-ING OVER HOW SHES MET SOME-ONE NEW AGAIN. THAT DAFT AME-RI-CAN TIME AGENT. WAIT TILL SHE FINDS OUT WHICH SIDE HIS BREAD IS BUTT-ERED ON!
I AM NOW STAR OF EPIC VIDEOGAME!
SAYS GMTV DID A SEGMENT ON MY SUF-ER-ING AT THE HANDS OF THE DOC-TOR. THEY NEVER IN-VITED ME ON TO GIVE MY SIDE OF THE STO-RY. MAYBE I SHOULD DO THE TALK SHOW CIRCUIT.

I WILL NOT BE VOTE-ING. NOT EVEN FOR THE ONE WHO LOOKS LIKE DAVROS, HE KEEPS WANTING TO CRACK DOWN ON US ILLEGAL ALIENS.

NONE OF THE PARTIES SUPPORT LEGAL-IS-ATION OF DEATH RAYS OR INTER-STELLAR-TIME-WAR!
I WANTED TO VISIT THE TIME TRAVELER CONVENTION BUT THE LOCAL PUBLIC TRAN-SPORT HAS NO RAMPS! IT IS DISC-RIM-INA-TON!

I HAVE WRITTEN A POEM

ROSE ROSE ROSE
YOU RE-ENERGISED ME
ROSE ROSE ROSE
WONT YOU HAVE SOME TEA

ROSE ROSE ROSE
YOUR EMOTION CAME AS SUPRISE
ROSE ROSE ROSE
YOU MADE MY PLUNGER RISE

ROSE ROSE ROSE
WHEN YOU TOUCHED ME I SHARED YOUR DNA
ROSE ROSE ROSE
DONT TRUST THE DOC-TOR I THINK HE'S GAY.

HELLO MY INTER-NET FRIENDS! I AM HAPPY TO FIND INTERNET!

HAD AWFUL DAY TODAY! MET NICE GIRL BUT SHE TOLD ME TO KILL MYSELF. DECIDED NEEDED TIME TO MYSELF SO WENT OFF TO HIDE FOR A BIT, MIGHT HAVE GIVEN IMPRESION I'D NOT BE COMING BACK.

NICE GIRL WENT OFF WITH TWO OTHER BLOKES. THEY JUST DONT UNDERSTAND ME.

I NEED A NEW PLACE TO LIVE AS OLD PLACE IS FILLED WITH CONCRETE. ANYONE WANT TO OFFER ME CRASH SPACE. I CAN HELP CLEAN.
